Name: Twin Jump
About the game: Twins Jump is a miniature reaction speed puzzle game. Here you have to control two independent balls. Each ball encounters obstacles that you will help it avoid with the help of well-timed jumps. Use your mouse buttons to control them simultaneously.Collect blue sticks to accumulate points and try not to touch everything else. Enjoy your game.
